    <description>When account is updated to cancelled customer, update onboarding fields in CF record and auto complete open tasks
08/09/2023 - PE - Updated the flow to move all open opportunities to &quot;Close Lost&quot; status when associated with an account that has been changed to the &quot;Cancelled Customer&quot; type. (Sprint 14 - 2023)
08/22/2023 - PE - Updated the flow to move open cases to &quot;Close Lost&quot; status when associated with an account that has been changed to the &quot;Cancelled Customer&quot; type. (Sprint 15 - 2023)
11/04/2024 - Updated to exclude Cancel Request Cases with origin of Failed Payment ( CRFP Cases) from auto closing .
1/16/24 JH - Updated to exclude EC Opps from being marked as CL so they remain open
04/07/25 - PE - Removed Proactivate Engagement Offline Payers cases from being canceled
04/11/25 - BW - Updated the Opp pull logic to only pull true open opps, not any in CW, CL, SSPR, etc
07/21/25 - PE - Added mapping to opportunity field PD Closed Lost Reason to prevent firing VR.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <description>Updates the field Closed Lost Reason on Billing Upsell opportunities to &quot;Canceled Saas&quot;. If other record type, does nothing.</description>
        <name>BillingUpsellCLReason</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
{!Loop_on_Opportunities.RecordTypeId} = &quot;0123u000000aNBlAAM&quot; /* Billing Upsell */,
&quot;Canceled Saas&quot;,
&quot;&quot;
)</expression>
    </formulas>
